@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

box "App Process" #White
participant "App (Activity)" as App #LightSkyBlue
end box

box "Framework Base (Modified by Mega)" #White
participant "Activity.java\n(Framework)" as FW_Activity #FFE4B5
participant "PackageManager.java\n(Framework)" as FW_PM #FFE4B5
end box

box "Mega Custom Permission UI" #White
participant "GrantPermissionsActivity\n(com.mega...)" as MegaUI #LightGreen
participant "PermissionRequestVM" as VM #LightGreen
participant "SysPermissionUtilsKt" as SysUtils #LightGreen
end box

box "AOSP Core Services" #White
participant "PackageManagerService\n(PMS)" as PMS #LightSkyBlue
participant "AppOpsManager" as AppOps #LightSkyBlue
end box

== 阶段 1：请求发起与拦截重定向 (Framework 层) ==
App -> FW_Activity : requestPermissions(permissions, requestCode)
activate FW_Activity

note over FW_Activity #FFE4B5
  **[Mega Porting]** 检查 permissions
  跳过以 "#" 开头的 permission
end note

FW_Activity -> FW_PM : buildRequestPermissionsIntent(permissions)
activate FW_PM

note over FW_PM #FFE4B5
  **[Mega Porting]** 解析 "#" 提取 moduleName，并从数组过滤。
  设置包名为 getMegaPermissionGrantPackageName()
end note

FW_PM --> FW_Activity : Intent (ACTION_REQUEST_PERMISSIONS)
deactivate FW_PM

FW_Activity -> MegaUI : startActivityForResult(intent)
note right of FW_Activity : 跨进程拉起 Mega 定制的授权 UI
FW_Activity --> App : 返回
deactivate FW_Activity


== 阶段 2：定制 UI 渲染与用户交互 (Mega 层) ==
activate MegaUI
note over MegaUI #LightGreen
  onCreate() 解析 Intent，绑定 ViewModel，渲染 UI
  *(等待用户点击允许/拒绝)*
end note

... 用户点击 "允许 (Allow)" ...

MegaUI -> MegaUI : setResultAndFinish()
MegaUI -> VM : setResultIfNeeded(activity, code=-1, needFinish=true)
activate VM


== 阶段 3：底层状态强行写入 (Mega Utils -> AOSP Service) ==
note over VM #LightGreen
  遍历 targetPkg 需要授予的权限 (如 LOCATION)
end note

VM -> SysUtils : updatePkgPermission(targetPkg, permStr, curUser, PermOp.Runtime, ...)
activate SysUtils

SysUtils -> PMS : grantRuntimePermission(targetPkg, permStr, user)
note right of PMS #LightSkyBlue : **[AOSP 原生 API]**\n向 PMS 写入该包名的运行时权限

SysUtils -> PMS : updatePermissionFlags(...)
note right of PMS #LightSkyBlue : **[AOSP 原生 API]**\n更新 USER_SET 等标志位

SysUtils -> AppOps : permissionToOp(permStr)
AppOps --> SysUtils : strPermissionToOp

SysUtils -> PMS : getPackageUidAsUser(targetPkg, userId)
PMS --> SysUtils : packageUidAsUser (如 UID 1000)

SysUtils -> AppOps : unsafeCheckOpRaw(...)
AppOps --> SysUtils : mode

SysUtils -> AppOps : setUidMode(strPermissionToOp, packageUidAsUser, 0 /* MODE_ALLOWED */)
note right of AppOps #LightSkyBlue : **[AOSP 原生 API]**\n**核心突破点：**\n基于 UID (1000) 强行放行 AppOps

SysUtils --> VM : Success
deactivate SysUtils

== 阶段 4：回调构造与完成 ==
VM -> PMS : checkPermission(permStr, targetPkg)
note right of VM #LightGreen : 再次向底座查验权限状态
PMS --> VM : PERMISSION_GRANTED

note over VM #LightGreen
  构造 resultIntent：
  putExtra(EXTRA_REQUEST_PERMISSIONS_NAMES, ...)
  putExtra(EXTRA_REQUEST_PERMISSIONS_RESULTS, ...)
end note

VM -> MegaUI : activity.setResult(-1, resultIntent)
VM -> MegaUI : activity.finishAfterTransition()

note over VM #LightGreen
  发送广播: OTHER_USER_NEED_UPDATE_ACTION
end note

deactivate VM

MegaUI --> FW_Activity : onActivityResult()
deactivate MegaUI

FW_Activity -> App : onRequestPermissionsResult(..., GRANTED)
note right of App #LightSkyBlue : App 获取到授权成功的最终回调
@enduml